ctrl + 1 : 				quick fix
ctrl + o : 				for quick outline going quicly to a method
ctrl + shift + w : 		closing all the files
ctrl + l : 				go to line
ctrl + shift + f : 		select text and format
ctrl + d : 				delete a line
ctrl + q : 				for going to last edited place
ctrl + shift + enter : 	insert a line above the current line
ctrl + shift + o : 		automatically insert needed imports
ctrl + space + r : 		opens the content assist window
